🐗🤸🏻‍♀️ @razorbackgym Head Coach ❤️
🥇 Olympic Gold Medalist
🎙 Speaker & Advocate 
📩 For speaking inquiries: denege@stanton-company.com

node.text: I'm so excited to be going Live this Saturday, July 10th at 12 PM CST/ 1 PM ET with @olay to talk to you about my story and an amazing opportunity to support women athletes! Be sure to set your reminder so you can join me live! #olayfaceofstrength

node.text: #Throwback to the 2012 Olympic Trials when my dreams came true! (Cue the ugly crying😝) Can’t wait to watch who will represent Team USA in Tokyo! Tune into #GymTrials21 on NBC, NBCSN and Peacock beginning tonight! @nbcolympics

node.text:
✨As the 2021 season has come to a close, I am overwhelmed with gratitude. What an incredible season of growth, challenges, and successes. This year was not easy, but absolutely worth every sacrifice that it took to not only have a healthy and safe season through a pandemic, but set multiple program records. This team grew in more ways than I can count, both as athletes and as human beings. Thank you to all that made it possible, thank you to Razorback nation for your support, and THANK YOU to our seniors, @sophiacarter, @sayshaff, @peggyjoe16, and @gymbacksyd for all you have done for this program! 

Wooo pig ❤️🐗

node.text: Christmas looks a little bit different this year. Staying in our own bubble in Fayetteville and it’s the first time I’ve ever been away from my family during the holidays. Although it’s hard, I’m SO grateful for this guy and for all of our blessings! ❤️🎄 Merry Christmas Eve!
